该游戏收获了评论家的一致好评。根据[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的12条评论，游戏的平均得分为75分（满分100分）<ref name=Metacritic />。根据[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]上的5条评论，得分为87%<ref name=GameRankings />。除此之外，该游戏还被[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]评为2011年50个最佳应用程序之一<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2044480_2043594_2043582,00.html|title=50 Best iPhone Apps 2011|last=Starr|first=Miral|date=2011-01-27|magazine=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|access-date=2011-01-27|archive-date=2013-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824005512/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2044480_2043594_2043582,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

评论家在游戏的整体趣味性上的意见大多数是统一的。[[IGN|IGN]]的Levi Buchanan表示这款游戏很有趣，而且他重复了三遍。除此之外，他认为这款游戏是有“即时性乐趣的”<ref name="ign review"/>Slide to Play的Chris Reed同意这个观点并表示这款游戏非常适合那些有短暂无聊的消费者。比如在排队等候的时候，“这似乎能将时间缩短一半”<ref name="slidetoplay review" />。[[GameZebo|GameZebo]]的Jim Squires认为这款游戏简单且让人上瘾<ref name="gamezebo review">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamezebo.com/iphone-games/fruit-ninja/review |publisher=[[GameZebo|GameZebo]] |access-date=2010-12-22 |date=2010-05-13 |first=Jim |last=Squires |title=Fruit Ninja Review |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6COT6iHjd?url=http://www.gamezebo.com/games/fruit-ninja/review |archive-date=2012-11-23 }}</ref>。DIYGamer的Geoff Gibson认为《水果忍者》将变为App Store的一件大事<ref name="diygamer review">{{Cite web|url=http://www.diygamer.com/2010/04/smoothie-fruit-ninja-review/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100427000643/http://www.diygamer.com/2010/04/smoothie-fruit-ninja-review/  |archive-date=2010-04-27 |title=Can I Get a Smoothie? Fruit Ninja Review |date=2010-04-21 |first=Geoff |last=Gibson |publisher=DIYGamer |access-date=2010-12-22 }}</ref>。一些评论家称赞了游戏价格和Halfbrick承诺对游戏的不断更新。 GameZone的James Pikover表示“也许最棒的部分是这款游戏还依旧没有完成”<ref name="gamezone review" />。然后他还谈到了未来可用的游戏模式以及对游戏性价比的同意<ref name="gamezone review" />。App Spy的Andrew Nesvadba对Halfbrick的承诺表示同意认为游戏的更新简直无与伦比<ref name="appspy review" />，另外，他还表扬了游戏的图形设计并称之为“甜美的”<ref name="appspy review" />。BuzzFocus的评论家表扬了游戏便宜的价格并且对消费者说"真的应该马上下载这款游戏<ref name="buzzfocus review">{{Cite web|url=http://www.buzzfocus.com/2010/04/25/iphone-review-fruit-ninja/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100428223351/http://www.buzzfocus.com/2010/04/25/iphone-review-fruit-ninja/  |archive-date=2010-04-28 |author=Bags |date=2010-04-25 |access-date=2010-12-22 |title=iPhone Game Review: Fruit Ninja |publisher=BuzzFocus }}</ref>。

===销售===
iOS版本的《水果忍者》在发售第一个月便售出了超过20万份<ref name="joystiq interview">{{Cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/05/10/halfbrick-shares-fruit-ninja-sales-numbers-how-to-succeed-on-th/ |publisher=Joystiq |access-date=2010-12-22 |title=Halfbrick shares Fruit Ninja sales numbers, how to succeed on the App store |first=David |last=Hinkle |date=2010-05-10 |archive-date=2012-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018191634/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/05/10/halfbrick-shares-fruit-ninja-sales-numbers-how-to-succeed-on-th/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三个月售出超过100万份<ref name="gamasutra million">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/60564/FRUIT_NINJA_SELLS_ONE_MILLION_COPIES_WORLDWIDE_ON_IPHONE_ANDIPOD_TOUCH.php|title=FRUIT NINJA SELLS ONE MILLION COPIES WORLDWIDE ON IPHONE AND IPOD TOUCH|date=2010-07-05|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|access-date=2010-12-22|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715012908/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/60564/FRUIT_NINJA_SELLS_ONE_MILLION_COPIES_WORLDWIDE_ON_IPHONE_ANDIPOD_TOUCH.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年9月，该作已售出200万份。2010年12月，销售量达到了400万<ref name="two million">{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/09/23/fruit-ninja-sells-two-million/|title=Fruit Ninja sells two million|last=McElroy|first=Justin|date=2010-09-23|publisher=Joystiq|access-date=2010-12-22|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018191639/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/09/23/fruit-ninja-sells-two-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截止2011年3月，全平台下载量超过2000万<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/03/03/fruit-ninja-surpasses-20-million-total-downloads/|title=Fruit Ninja surpasses 20 million total downloads|last=Hinkle|first=David|date=2011-03-03|publisher=Joystiq|access-date=2011-03-09|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629131745/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/03/03/fruit-ninja-surpasses-20-million-total-downloads/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年5月，该作达到了3亿次的下载量，全美三分之一的iPhone用户都下载过这款游戏<ref name="downloads @ May 31, 2012">{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/31/fruit-ninja-tops-300m-downloads-after-two-years-now-installed-on-13-of-all-u-s-iphones/|title=Fruit Ninja Tops 300M+ Downloads After Two Years, Now Installed On 1/3 Of All U.S. iPhones|last=Crook|first=Jordan|date=2012-05-31|publisher=TechCrunch|work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|access-date=2012-07-01|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029060612/https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/31/fruit-ninja-tops-300m-downloads-after-two-years-now-installed-on-13-of-all-u-s-iphones/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，下载量达到10亿次<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://kotaku.com/fruit-ninjas-creators-have-been-split-by-an-identity-cr-1788685803|title=Fruit Ninja's Creators Have Been Split By An Identity Crisis|last=Serrels|first=Mark|work=Kotaku|access-date=2017-06-26|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401065957/https://kotaku.com/fruit-ninjas-creators-have-been-split-by-an-identity-cr-1788685803|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

